<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Antonio Carrasco Hiruelo" .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A comprehensive ontology representing high-risk medical devices, their manufacturers, associated risks, incident reports, and field safety corrective actions (FSCAs), based on the European MDR and IVDR regulatory frameworks." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "EUDAMED Medical Devices Ontology" .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0" .
