<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a Field Safety Corrective Action (FSCA) to the underlying incident it aims to resolve." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "addresses incident" .
# 
