<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#compliesWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#compliesWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Device> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#compliesWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Regulation> .
