<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Incident> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Risk> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a reported incident to the specific risk category or hazard that caused it." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has associated risk" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Device> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Manufacturer> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a medical device to its unique manufacturer responsible for its regulatory compliance." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has manufacturer" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
