<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Device> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#RiskClass> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a medical device to its assigned regulatory risk class under MDR or IVDR." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has risk class" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Incident> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Device> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an adverse incident report to the specific medical device involved in the event." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#involvesDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "involves device" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
