<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Country> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the geographical country where the manufacturer's headquarters is located." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#locatedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "located in" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#requiresManufacturerInvestigation
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#requiresManufacturerInvestigation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
