<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#requiresManufacturerInvestigation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Manufacturer> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#requiresManufacturerInvestigation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An inferred relationship indicating that a specific manufacturer must investigate the linked incident. Populated by SWRL rule." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#requiresManufacturerInvestigation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "requires manufacturer investigation" .
# 
# http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#targetsDevice
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#targetsDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
