<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#targetsDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Device> .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#targetsDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An inferred relationship connecting a Field Safety Corrective Action directly to the targeted medical device. Populated by SWRL rule." .
<http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#targetsDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "targets device" .
